{"tid":1767050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳鄭若驊低調回港     林鄭：不便透露對方個人私隱","createTime":"2019-12-03T04:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T09:30:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e97e95c866d99838a091a62157ad4f5590826b3d","tid":1767050,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊上月中在英國倫敦被示威者包圍抗議，混亂間跌倒左手腕脫臼兼骨折。對於有傳鄭若驊已經低調回港，行政長官林鄭月娥表示，鄭若驊目前仍在放病假，不便透露對方個人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊上月中在遇襲後向倫敦警察報案，並要求當地警方嚴肅跟進將兇徒繩之於法。她早前稱其左手腕脫臼兼骨折，需要安裝鈦版固定位置。她又引述醫生稱其左手未能正常活動至少3個月至1年，可能傷及神經，需要進行手術。林鄭月娥事後對事件感憤慨，並指襲擊行為野蠻，超越文明社會底線。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1651777/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%82%B3%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E4%BD%8E%E8%AA%BF%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%BB%8D%E5%9C%A8%E6%94%BE%E7%97%85%E5%81%87</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7e9e872cf0ca6ac19a3800eb4da551ec0622df2d","tid":1767050,"uid":156144,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:41:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老味呢個時候就講私隱"},{"pid":"a6bfb3b71cc7ca6802929d71e31bd9c1527ada6b","tid":1767050,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"deal已傾"},{"pid":"946d9226ff3b905d54fabaf83d21b25369694962","tid":1767050,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"可能已經客死異鄉"},{"pid":"c0b9c5b4165819fcc2975092fe243d8d85b625fa","tid":1767050,"uid":261332,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"個肥婆扮傷就係99%事實啦，咁究竟扮傷係為咩？<br />\n如果係為自己後路打點，林鄭就唔會仲攬佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n即係話佢係幫埋林鄭打點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938d40ec553fb38dc8e65dd88829e54ae86d2e27","tid":1767050,"uid":279981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime